{"tid":32184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（求祝福）黑到一個極點","createTime":"2016-12-10T05:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T16:02:25.000Z","uid":14175,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"950d2e690dc70bbcee97b7b0be17504ac99f59ce","tid":32184,"uid":14175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:11:33.000Z","msg":"呢排真係好黑仔<br />\n先係同女朋友六年感情差啲完 暫時叫冇事<br />\n之後到阿叔身體有事 <br />\n早幾日岩岩過身<br />\n今日又到阿嫲入咗醫院<br />\n醫生估計快則今晚走<br />\n最遲都係三四日左右<br />\n雖然同阿叔阿嫲感情唔係話好好<br />\n但始終都係一家人 始終都好唔知點咁<br />\n成個人做咩都冇心情 人其實真係好化學<br />\n見到老豆呢排冇晒心情<br />\n又做唔到啲咩 唯有收工後多啲陪佢<br />\n各位巴打絲打記得珍惜眼前人<br />\n樹欲靜而風不息<br />\n子欲養而親不在"},{"pid":"e5fbe4ece210a9b522774fd6ea4b3aa742d8a595","tid":32184,"uid":15797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:16:11.000Z","msg":"撐住巴打....兩年前同你差不多狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a2e8e5f58bc301ab484bd39702776670777114","tid":32184,"uid":54878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"咁就叫黑到極點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又未分手，死嘅又唔係直屬親人<br />\n睇黎你平時應該好好運"},{"pid":"dbb721e10ce3affcb5ff285673e47407adfb7b4d","tid":32184,"uid":14175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撐住巴打....兩年前同你差不多狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收通宵去醫院探病<br />\n咁上下諗住返屋企沖個涼抖下再出去<br />\n搭車果陣又遇著撞車 塞咗半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582dae34be4ebd8d3559167ed891ac40c2832ec2","tid":32184,"uid":11819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.